<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 -1-
 ạnt
 ḥqyqy̱ ạ̹lh ḥnyn ... kl ạ̉ḥzạny tsẖyl wthawĩn
 lmạ bab̊ʿid ạnt tqrãb ... kl ạnyny
 tzyl wtṭm̃n
 ạlqrạr- ạywẗ baḥky ʿnk wbaqwl ạnt rby
 kl ạfrạḥy mnk wḥdk sạkn qlby
 -2-
 wạnt
 ạlʿạly bqyt ạ̹nsạn ... ʿlsẖạn tqr̃b mny kmạn
 lmạ bakẖṭī̉ ʿlyã btṣbr ... wtrj̃ʿny
 bkl ḥnạn
 -3-
 msw̉wl
 ʿny fy kl ạḥwạly ... ạnqdẖtny wḍmnt ḥyạty
 ʿn mjdk jyt wtnạzlt ... lạnk ạnt
 ḥạss bạ̉ḥwạly
 -4-
 wftḥt
 ly ạbwạb ạlsmạʾ ... wfzt bkl sʿạdẗ whanạ
 bfḍl ậlạmk ạnt yạ rby ... wʿạysẖ
 bfḍl ḥbk hinạ
 -5-
 llạ̉qdạs
 dkẖlt bdm̃k ... ṣrt ạbwya wbqyt ạbnk
 ṣạlḥtny wkmlt kẖlạṣy ... wsmḥt ly
 ạqrb mnk</lyrics>
